dct_title_s: Irland = Ireland = Irlande = Irlanda = Irlandii͡a / Reise Know-How.
dct_description_sm: Shows roads, railways, natural features and tourist features. Relief shown by contours, gradient tints, and spot heights. Depth shown by gradient tints and isolines. "Projektion: Lambert Conformal / Ellipsoid WGS 84"--Upper left margin. Ancillary map: Skellig Islands. Includes index of places, coverage map, color illustrations, and publisher's advertisement.
